myVelibCLUI

Class Interface

  • java.lang.Object
    • myVelibCLUI.Interface

  • public class Interface
extends java.lang.Object
    Interface is the console provider of the CLUI. It contains all the description, name and number of arguments of commands. Its main method receives command runtest and checks the conformity of commands before sending to Processing.
    Author:
    Ahmed Djermani
